  - {fileID: 1528981677}
  - {fileID: 1607959752}
  - {fileID: 968917018}
  - {fileID: 1717512001}
  subtitles:
  - Every book has a soul. But some stories are more alive than others.
  - I just wanted to read one more chapter. But the pages... they were violently
    torn out. The story was bleeding.
  - Before I could understand, the words pulled me in. The ink became my reality
  - Now, I am the story. And if I don't find the lost pages... this world will fade
    into nothing.
  subtitleTextUI: {fileID: 1549449489}
  nextSceneName: Level_1
